\b High Voltage Safety Block\b0\par
\par
When working with high voltage equipment:\par
\bullet  Verify voltage is below 50V before touching any conductors\par
\bullet  Use insulated tools rated for the voltage level\par
\bullet  Wear appropriate PPE (class 00 or higher rubber gloves)\par
\bullet  Have a second qualified person present when required by site procedures\par
\par
